description: Demolition of existing building and erection of a building ranging in height from 7 - 15 storeys, consisting of 2,509m basement parking and plant, a parking permit-free proposal for 129 residential flats (37 one-bedroom, 73 two-bedroom, 19 three-bedroom), a 5,837m 125-bedroom hotel (Use Class C1), 1,983m of community swimming-pool and fitness facilities (Use Class D2), and associated landscaping, as amendedPlanning Act 1990 and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 9th April 2010 under Section 106 of the Town and Country, as amended
